commentary: Rampaul to Mohammad Ashraful, OUT Ashraful is on his way already. Blink-and-you-miss innings. Nice lively bouncer from Rampaul, Ashraful goes for a shot he wouldn't have tried if it wasn't the Powerplay, or if the situation wasn't so difficult (though, with Ashraful, it is tough to say). He's cramped for the pull and  Ramdin takes the top edge.

commentary: Pollard to Shakib Al Hasan, SIX runs Shakib should try his hand at golf. He's skipped out, got to the length of a ball and drove it through the line, taking the bottom hand off to ensure he didn't pollute the stroke. A thing of beauty, it sailed over long-off.
